---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="홈">
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary to-secondary py-16 px-4">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto text-center text-white">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">AI, 누구나 쓸 수 있습니다</h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl opacity-90 mb-8">도구 추천부터 바이브코딩 강좌까지, AI 활용의 모든 것</p>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
        <a href="/courses" class="bg-white text-primary font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-100">무료 강좌 시작</a>
        <a href="/tools" class="border-2 border-white text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10">AI 도구 보기</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">🔥 이번 주 AI 도구 픽</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-2">💬</div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-sm">ChatGPT</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">대화형 AI 어시스턴트</p>
        <span class="inline-block mt-2 text-xs bg-blue-100 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">무료+유료</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🎨</div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-sm">Midjourney</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">AI 이미지 생성</p>
        <span class="inline-block mt-2 text-xs bg-purple-100 text-secondary px-2 py-1 rounded">유료</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-2">📝</div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-sm">Notion AI</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">문서 작성 보조</p>
        <span class="inline-block mt-2 text-xs bg-blue-100 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">무료+유료</span>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl p-4 hover:shadow-lg transition">
        <div class="text-3xl mb-2">🎵</div>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-sm">Suno AI</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">AI 음악 생성</p>
        <span class="inline-block mt-2 text-xs bg-green-100 text-accent px-2 py-1 rounded">무료</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">💰 AI 지원사업</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <a href="/grants" class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-lg transition block">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
            <span class="text-xs bg-blue-100 text-primary px-2 py-1 rounded">보조금</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-red-500 font-bold">D-30</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mt-3">AI 바우처 지원사업</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">정보통신산업진흥원</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2">최대 3억원 지원</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/grants" class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-lg transition block">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
            <span class="text-xs bg-purple-100 text-secondary px-2 py-1 rounded">R&D</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-red-500 font-bold">D-15</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mt-3">AI 융합 혁신인재 양성</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">과학기술정보통신부</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2">교육비 전액 지원</p>
        </a>
        <a href="/grants" class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-lg transition block">
          <div class="flex justify-between items-start">
            <span class="text-xs bg-green-100 text-accent px-2 py-1 rounded">데이터</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-orange-500 font-bold">D-45</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-bold mt-3">데이터바우처 지원사업</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-1">한국데이터산업진흥원</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2">최대 7천만원 지원</p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">📚 인기 AI 강좌</h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
      <a href="/courses" class="group block">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-500 to-blue-700 rounded-xl p-6 text-white group-hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <span class="text-xs bg-white/20 px-2 py-1 rounded">입문</span>
          <h3 class="font-bold mt-3 text-lg">바이브코딩이란?</h3>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-80 mt-2">AI에게 말로 설명하면 코드가 완성되는 새로운 개발 방식</p>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/courses" class="group block">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-purple-500 to-purple-700 rounded-xl p-6 text-white group-hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <span class="text-xs bg-white/20 px-2 py-1 rounded">실습</span>
          <h3 class="font-bold mt-3 text-lg">ChatGPT로 웹사이트 만들기</h3>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-80 mt-2">0원으로 내 웹사이트를 만들고 배포하는 전 과정</p>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="/courses" class="group block">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-500 to-teal-700 rounded-xl p-6 text-white group-hover:shadow-lg transition">
          <span class="text-xs bg-white/20 px-2 py-1 rounded">활용</span>
          <h3 class="font-bold mt-3 text-lg">프롬프트 엔지니어링 입문</h3>
          <p class="text-sm opacity-80 mt-2">AI에게 정확히 원하는 결과를 얻는 질문법</p>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-gray-50 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-6">📰 오늘의 AI 뉴스</h2>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <a href="/news" class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition">
          <span class="text-2xl">🏛️</span>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-sm">인공지능으로 통화 중 보이스피싱 잡는다</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">과학기술정보통신부 · 2시간 전</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/news" class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition">
          <span class="text-2xl">🌾</span>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-sm">스마트농업, AI로 새로운 진화를 꿈꾸다</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">정책브리핑 · 5시간 전</p>
          </div>
        </a>
        <a href="/news" class="flex items-center gap-4 bg-white rounded-xl p-4 border border-gray-200 hover:shadow-md transition">
          <span class="text-2xl">🔬</span>
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-sm">온디바이스 AI 반도체 개발 집중 지원</h3>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 mt-1">과학기술정보통신부 · 어제</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 text-center">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">🚀 AI 활용, 지금 시작하세요</h2>
    <p class="text-gray-500 mb-6">매일 업데이트되는 AI 도구, 강좌, 지원사업 정보를 받아보세요</p>
    <a href="/courses" class="bg-primary text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 inline-block">무료 강좌 시작하기</a>
  </section>
</Layout>
